<TEXT>
 Homosexual or bisexual males: 37,159, or 63 percent. Intravenous drug abusers: 10,627, or 18 percent. Homosexual male and drug abusers: 4,325, or 7 percent. Heterosexual cases: 2,392, or 4 percent. Transfusion or blood cases: 1,556, or 3 percent. Hemophilia patients: 634, or 1 percent Undetermined transmission cause: 1,877, or 3 percent
