<HEAD>Meese Aide Decries GOP Senators' `Litmus Test' on Bork</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By PETE YOST</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
